>>>> two arguments expect different things" than "this one argument expects a
>>>> different thing depending on the value of another argument".
>>>>
>>>> -Ryan
>>>>
>>>>
>>>> On Sun Jun 15 11:17:59 2014, Michael Lawrence wrote:
